# Ignore patterns for OpenCode
# These directories are excluded from search to reduce noise and improve relevance

# Build outputs and caches
**/dist/**
**/.next/**
**/.turbo/**
**/coverage/**
**/.cache/**
**/node_modules/**

# Generated files
**/.DS_Store/**
**/*.log
**/tmp/**

# Lock files (unless explicitly requested)
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock

# Environment files
**/.env*
**/.envrc

# IDE files
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**

# OS files
**/Thumbs.db